1.0.1.name: wordpress/add-logo-to-admin
1.0.1.description: This plugin allows a user to customize their Admin panel by adding their own logo to the header. It also replaces the WordPress logo on the login screen with the same custom logo. Tested in Firefox, Safari, Chrome and IE.
